						<summary>

						<p>On the west wall of the Kuraṅganātha temple.</p>						

						<p>Kulōttuṅga I. Year 21: 1090-91 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record commences with the <hi rend="italic">praśasti Pugaḻmādu viḷaṅga</hi>, etc., of Kulōttuṅga I.</p>						

						<p>This mentions Mīmalai Jayaṅgoṇḍaśōḻa-chchaturvēdimaṅgalam and <hi rend="italic">Rājēndrapperunteru.</hi> Other details are lost.</p>						

